import CSS from "csstype";

export const borderedStyle: CSS.Properties = {
    border: "2px",
    borderColor: "black",
    borderStyle: "solid",
    borderRadius: "25px",
    padding: "16px",
    margin: "10px",
    flex: 1,
    backgroundColor: "#a7cae8",
    height: "500px"
}
